Package: HiSpaR
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Inference of Spatial Positions from Hi-C Data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-01-15
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Contributors", "Names", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: HiSpaR provides R bindings for HiSpa, a Hierarchical Bayesian model 
    for inferring 3D chromatin structures from Hi-C contact matrices using MCMC sampling.
    The package uses Rcpp and RcppArmadillo for efficient C++ integration with the 
    original HiSpa C++ implementation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    methods
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
SystemRequirements: 
    C++17,
    GNU make,
    Armadillo (>= 9.0),
    OpenMP
URL: https://github.com/masterStormtrooper/HiSpa
